channel.title: Concord Baptist Church Video Podcast
channel.description:
This podcast features messages from Concord Baptist of Clermont Georgia. Thank you for visiting! If you were to ever visit Concord, here are a few things that you would find:

Godâ€™s Word believed and then boldly and enthusiastically proclaimed.
Exciting Worship Services that are relevant and memorable.
Small group Bible studies that are biblically based, meaningful, and friendly.
Children / Student ministries designed to support parents and prepare students.
A Missions emphasis to reach out to our community and the ends of the world.

Is this a tall order? You bet! But here at Concord this challenge is also embedded into our vision statement. This list is also what recent members said drew them to unite with this unique fellowship. Are these suggestions what you are looking for? Look no further because Concord Baptist Church is the place for you! This church desires to live by the principles of the Word of God, to be led by the Spirit of God, and to lift up the Son of God. If you would like more information about Concord please visit our web site at www.concordministries.net

Thanks again and enjoy the podcast!
